These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea, orchid
1. the person who growsazalea is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | juice   |
| Flower      | balloon-flower    | azalea  | orchid |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, mechanic, software-developer
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian
1. the argentine is on the left of the software-developer##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the canadian is the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job      | mechanic | photographer     | software-developer      |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, water
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, townhouse
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the townhouse house##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water  | tea       |
| House       | craftsman     | gothic-revival | townhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, radish, zucchini
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, indian, argentine
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the argentine##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the indonesian##1
3. the argentine is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | zucchini    | radish     | pomegranate |
| Nationality   | argentine | indonesian | indian     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hedgehog
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, camping, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is camping is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | bird     | hedgehog |
| Hobby   | video-games        | photography | camping    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
3 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, bridge
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person playing bridge is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Game        | bridge | canasta      | monopoly  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, salsa
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, subway, van
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of r&b is the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | jazz     | r&b    |
| Transport           | trike | van | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, thai
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the argentine##1
2. the thai is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the chinese is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality    | thai | argentine | chinese      |
| Hobby   | camping     | skydiving | card-games |

