.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, puzzles
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bluemaster, blend
1. the montecristo-smoker is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | filmmaking | chess  |
| Cigar     | blend     | montecristo      | bluemaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, tea
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, raspberry, lettuce
1. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person eating lettuce is on the far right##1
3. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | cola   | sprite    | tea    |
| Food   | raspberry | broccoli | lettuce |

