.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, march, july
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, german
1. the person who's birthday is in july is the canadian##1
2. the canadian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the german is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Birthday   | april | july   | march  |
| Nationality   | german    | canadian | dutch |

