.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, electrician, security-guard
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, begonia, marigold
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the security-guard is on the left of the electrician##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | coach    | security-guard | electrician |
| Flower   | marigold | dahlia     | begonia        |

