.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, black, red
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, pop
1. the person who likes black is on the far right##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who likes black##1
3. the person who likes red is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Color      | lilac  | red | black  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | pop   | classical |

