.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-16::.
There 3 different types of food: spinach, pear, grapes
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, lawyer, pilot
1. the lawyer is on the far right##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating pear##1
3. the person eating pear is on the left of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Food   | pear | spinach | grapes    |
| Job        | coach    | pilot | lawyer |

