.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, singing, sudoku
3 different games are played: whist, billiard, mah-jongg
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | camping | singing | sudoku |
| Game   | whist | mah-jongg     | billiard  |

