.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, bird, lizard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, soccer
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Pet    | lizard | goat       | bird  |
| Sport   | soccer  | snowboarding | cycling |

 